{"tid":1856811,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Chinese President Xi Jinping Putin best friend 俄羅斯派軍機從中國撤走國民","createTime":"2020-02-01T21:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T00:27:01.000Z","uid":125193,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9c5943564dad5ae261300dd75614e07633ed3efc","tid":1856811,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T21:13:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506138-20200202.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506138-20200202.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=faf4b6e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506138-20200202.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9acb7ecd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506138-20200202.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯軍方將派遣飛機，從中國發生新型冠狀病毒的地區，撤走本國公民。<br />\n<br />\n國際文傳通訊社和塔斯社報道，將於星期一和星期二採取撤僑行動。克里姆林宮發言人表示，將會從疫情最嚴重的地區撤僑。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯至今有兩宗新型肺炎病例，患者都是中國公民，俄方已限制來往中國的直航航班。<br />\n<br />\n另外，俄羅斯政府停止給予中國公民免簽證旅遊待遇，並暫停發出工作簽證。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯政府說，這樣做是確保俄國安全，保障公眾健康以及防止新型冠狀病毒擴散。<br />\n<br />\n自2000年起，中國旅行團可獲豁免簽證到俄羅斯。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京早前致電國家主席習近平，就疫情表示慰問，又說願意向中國人民提供必要協助。"},{"pid":"2f6b5a599744ec32f2a791eb1d87013039bfade9","tid":1856811,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T22:34:33.000Z","msg":"軍機 已經係常識<br />\n唔到你中共講話唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為你啲武漢人走到全世界都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a0e77d9b58a3f2ff80dac2f2c857e1167658d2","tid":1856811,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T22:42:18.000Z","msg":"軍機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a2de7d3a5205c262f6ed1e31b82620016fb344","tid":1856811,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:27:01.000Z","msg":"你的老朋友啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}